h the long-range ordering of the Sm ions. Our\nresults show that the SMR is a sensitive technique for non-equilibrium spin\nsystem of non-collinear AFM systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jul 2019 03:27:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-12"}
